analysis: The agent used parameter values with initial capital letters ("Moderate", "Dynamic") instead of the expected lowercase ("moderate", "dynamic"), causing a mismatch with the function signature and resulting in no valid function call recognized by the evaluator.
The agent incorrectly set the "outputDetail" parameter to "Detailed" instead of the required "Summary," resulting in a function call mismatch with the expected answer.
The agent used "Comprehensive" instead of the expected "Detailed" for the detailLevel parameter. This mismatch prevented the function call from matching the expected parameters, leading to failure.

The agent incorrectly added an extra argument "weatherDetail" to the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch with the expected function signature that only accepts "airportCode" and "flightNumber".
The agent failed to include the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter when calling GameFinder_analyzeUserInterestForGames, missing the user's explicit request for games with good ratings.
The agent incorrectly used a numerical value ("4.5") for the "rating" parameter instead of the expected categorical value ("high"), causing the function call not to match the expected format.
